ActBudget Implementation Act, 2009
SubjectOrder Amending the Order Extending Export Development Canada's Temporary Domestic Powers
PrecisOrder extending EXPORT DEVELOPMENT CANADA'S TEMPORARY DOMESTIC POWERS in order to (1) allow for the necessary time to complete the regulatory process to support amendments to the Regulations; and (2) ensure some continuity in Export Development Canada's provision of domestic support.
